Type Property# canonicalPathKey

iOS 10.0+iPadOS 10.0+Mac Catalyst 13.1+macOS 10.12+tvOS 10.0+visionOS 1.0+watchOS 3.0+

```
static let canonicalPathKey: URLResourceKey
```

## [Discussion](/documentation/Foundation/URLResourceKey/canonicalPathKey#Discussion)

The URL’s path as a canonical absolute file system path, returned as an [`NSString`](/documentation/foundation/nsstring) object (read-only).
